        "title": "Thank You for Participating!",
        "description": "<div>Congratulations on completing this session. We’d love to hear your reflections on today’s experience—what stood out, what supported your learning, and how we can continue to improve.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>This short reflection <strong>will take less than 5 minutes</strong> and helps us ensure our sessions are impactful, relevant, and aligned with your goals.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Your honest feedback is essential. This is an opportunity to model authentic communication —your insights will help us shape and strengthen this learning journey together.</div>",
